data.description: Move in ready. New construction home with 1,545 square feet on one-story including 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and an open living area. Enjoy an open kitchen with 36” white shaker-style cabinets with crown moulding, Samsung stainless steel appliances, a walk-in pantry, and a spacious island, fully open to the dining café and gathering room. The living area, laundry room, and baths include luxury wood vinyl plank flooring, with stain-resistant carpet in the bedrooms. Your owner's suite is complete with a walk-in wardrobe and a private en-suite bath with dual vanities, a tiled shower, and a closeted toilet. Plus, enjoy a covered lanai, 2-car garage, custom-fit window blinds, architectural shingles, energy-efficient insulation and windows, and a full builder warranty.   "Please note, virtual tour/photos showcases the home layout; colors and design options in actual home for sale may differ. Furnishings and décor do not convey.”  SOCIAL DISTANCING AND/OR MASKS REQUIRED IN ALL MODELS
